{"tid":1651254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【極重要】完全解決日程表問題嘅方法","createTime":"2019-10-13T09:40:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T21:08:58.000Z","uid":311583,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"519d18269c87ff64a6661f1a7e11065c2520b6c0","tid":1651254,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:40:07.000Z","msg":"日程表好亂，一日有6,7個活動，點算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n需要搵一個人，例如高橋(777文宣傳播稿件大合集 <a href=\"http://t.me/hkposter777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkposter777&d=uxh%2FksCcDU8UuFRsnlXnuSbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=13309b0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkposter777</a> )，佢係日程表設計人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當你需要搞活動，就需要同高橋講，佢會負責<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幫你寫入日程表</span></span>同做文宣，但如果嗰個時間<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">已經有其他活動</span></span>出現，咁你就唔可以揀喺呢個時間搞活動，要搞就<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">揀其他時間</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n咁就可以避免d活動撞時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留意，高橋唔係大台，佢只不過係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人肉電腦</span></span></strong>，booking system.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例如我想喺10月20日8:00p.m.發起反蒙面法人鏈，你就要向高橋 book 10月20日 8:00p.m~10:00p.m. ，如果個時間之前有其他搞手book咗，高橋會話俾我聽，叫我book其他時間<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋，要預早一個星期book定，例如今日10月13日，就唔可以book10月13日至19日。<br />\n<br />\n如果有緊急活動(如10月4)，咁點算？<br />\n其實呢d活動唔駛寫入日程表，d人自然會黎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01509030df98e36566cda2bb044e2c9520bbeb18","tid":1651254,"uid":182491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:52:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4ec662c3455bfd773c85ec36a6692421a2838096","tid":1651254,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:52:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c34ab62d835a6c88121b0651cf4681face5d34d","tid":1651254,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:55:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4faf64ef811644caa2d255e2b2be2f1f2acd7514","tid":1651254,"uid":220045,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:00:17.000Z","msg":"其實撞時間呢d野<br />\n作為活動搞手都唔留意<br />\n而要靠一個整calendar既人去check<br />\n會唔會低質左小小<br />\n<br />\n而且一個整calendar既人只係應該整理活動基本資料 ie 時地人事<br />\n點可以決定活動時間？<br />\n因為有d活動既時間係有意思地安排<br />\n唔係話一定先到先得就啱<br />\n<br />\n個人認為呢d野應該要放上連登討論<br />\n而唔係單睇邊個提出活動先就決定果個時間邊個用"},{"pid":"d30805c357e08529fff05f05d7e95c65f1746bd0","tid":1651254,"uid":310805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:04:31.000Z","msg":"之前見過apple calendar link<br />\n有無人maintain緊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab27c82c26f652a02b3a02bdde0791663965dd0f","tid":1651254,"uid":182802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d30805c357e08529fff05f05d7e95c65f1746bd0","tid":1651254,"uid":310805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:04:31.000Z","msg":"之前見過apple calendar link<br />\n有無人maintain緊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:15:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UwUnu72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUwUnu72.jpg&h=0a334c11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db2fa4c60e8caef36f48c7b2de597ac76f69aaec","tid":1